        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Watch issued May 28 at 12:47AM CDT until May 28 at 8:00AM CDT by NWS Brownsville TX</headline>
        <description>THE NATIONAL WEATHER SERVICE HAS ISSUED SEVERE THUNDERSTORM WATCH
340 IN EFFECT UNTIL 8 AM CDT THIS MORNING FOR THE FOLLOWING AREAS

IN TEXAS THIS WATCH INCLUDES 8 COUNTIES

IN DEEP SOUTH TEXAS

BROOKS                CAMERON               HIDALGO
JIM HOGG              KENEDY                STARR
WILLACY               ZAPATA

THIS INCLUDES THE CITIES OF BROWNSVILLE, EDINBURG, FALFURRIAS,
HARLINGEN, HEBBRONVILLE, MCALLEN, MISSION, PHARR, RAYMONDVILLE,
RIO GRANDE CITY, ROMA, SARITA, WESLACO, AND ZAPATA.
</description>
